01:34.797 --> 01:36.265
- Don't move!
- Aah!

01:37.717 --> 01:39.560
- Gee!
- Charlie!

01:39.635 --> 01:41.228
What the hell are you doing?

01:41.429 --> 01:42.406
What the hell am I doing?

01:42.430 --> 01:44.565
What the hell are you doing
sneaking around the house?

01:45.683 --> 01:47.359
I forgot my keys, okay?

01:47.685 --> 01:49.361
Put down the knife, you idiot.

01:50.479 --> 01:51.623
It's three o'clock
in the morning.

01:51.647 --> 01:53.115
What the hell's going on?

01:53.482 --> 01:54.700
Nothing.

01:55.818 --> 01:57.453
Well, where have you been?

01:57.945 --> 01:59.747
- Out.
- Out where?

02:01.323 --> 02:02.300
Come on, Charlie.

02:02.324 --> 02:03.552
For the last, like, two weeks,

02:03.576 --> 02:04.928
I've been hearing you
come home every night

02:04.952 --> 02:06.263
at God knows what hour.

02:06.287 --> 02:07.973
You know, that's funny, 'cause
the last time I checked,

02:07.997 --> 02:09.340
I didn't have a curfew.

02:09.372 --> 02:10.475
Well, what... What
are you doing?

02:10.499 --> 02:13.552
You hanging out with a
group of guys after work?

02:14.754 --> 02:16.273
Are you seeing some new girl?

02:16.297 --> 02:17.556
You know what?

02:17.715 --> 02:18.942
I'm a whole lot older
than you are, Bay.

02:18.966 --> 02:20.225
I don't have to answer to you.

02:21.052 --> 02:23.354
You want to check on bedtimes,
check on Claudia's.

02:23.679 --> 02:24.980
Now go to bed.

02:25.556 --> 02:27.274
Something going on
with you, Charlie?

02:27.475 --> 02:28.650
Go to bed.

